              | In the future, the goal is not only to retrieve manga, anime or characters
              | by keywords, but also to
              em  infer
              |  and find related content, thanks to similarity matrices and semantic web.
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href="https://github.com/Sn0wFox/manmanga", target="_blank")
