              strong  Node.js, Typescript, Gulp, Angular2, Materialize, Pug, Sass, Webpack, Jasmine, Karma, Travis CI
              |  and some other cool Node packages. In a future release, it will also relies on some&nbsp;
              a(href="https://github.com/Sn0wFox/indexden-client", target="_blank") other projects of mine
              |  to avoid relying on Google.

    // SBT internship
    section.content.content-2#snfx-portfolio-sbt
      .container
        .row
          .col-sm-6.text-center
            h2.section-header My last Summer Internship
            p.lead.text-light.text-justify In summer 2016, I worked as an intern at&nbsp;
              a(href="http://www.sbt.fr/", target="_blank")
                strong SBT
                  sup &reg;
              |  in France as a
              strong  Web Developper
              | . As part of a great team, I had two missions:
            #accordion.panel-group(role='tablist', aria-multiselectable='true')
              .panel.panel-default
                #snfx-small-one.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title
                    a(role='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#snfx-collapse-one', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='snfx-collapse-one')
